>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MAIN.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 TOTAL PIC 9.
01 I PIC S9.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE TOTAL = 0
    IF 1 < 4
        PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I >= 4
            COMPUTE TOTAL = TOTAL + I
        END-PERFORM
    ELSE
        PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY -1 UNTIL I <= 4
            COMPUTE TOTAL = TOTAL + I
        END-PERFORM
    END-IF
    DISPLAY TOTAL
    STOP RUN.
